classDiagram
    class Task {
        +String description
        +String pet_name
        +String time
        +int duration_mins
        +String priority
        +String frequency
        +bool is_complete
        +Date due_date
        +mark_complete() void
        +start_minutes() int
    }
    note for Task "Validates on creation (__post_init__):
    time must be HH:MM, priority in {high, medium, low},
    frequency in {daily, weekly, monthly, once}"

    class Pet {
        +String name
        +String species
        +List~Task~ tasks
        +add_task(task) void
        +get_tasks() List~Task~
    }

    class Owner {
        +String name
        +List~Pet~ pets
        +add_pet(pet) void
        +get_all_pets() List~Pet~
    }

    class Scheduler {
        +Owner owner
        +get_todays_schedule() List~Task~
        +sort_by_time(tasks) List~Task~
        +sort_by_priority(tasks) List~Task~
        +filter_by_pet(tasks, pet_name) List~Task~
        +filter_by_status(tasks, is_complete) List~Task~
        +mark_task_complete(task) Task
        +check_conflicts(tasks) List~Pair~
        +conflict_warnings(tasks) List~String~
    }
    note for Scheduler "mark_task_complete() spawns the next
    occurrence of daily/weekly/monthly tasks
    (due_date = today + FREQUENCY_INTERVAL)"

    Owner "1" o-- "many" Pet : has
    Pet "1" o-- "many" Task : has
    Scheduler "1" --> "1" Owner : manages
    Scheduler ..> Pet : places recurring tasks
    Scheduler ..> Task : sorts, filters, completes
